OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover prepayment meters     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy suppliers should stop forcing   
OL,6, vulnerable households on to prepayment 
OL,7, meters, the government has said.       
OL,9,FBusiness Secretary Grant Shapps' warned
OL,10,Fhe would "name and shame" suppliers who
OL,11,Fwere doing "nowhere near enough" for   
OL,12,Fvulnerable customers.                  
OL,14,FThere have been calls for a ban on the 
OL,15,Fpractice from charities including      
OL,16,FCitizens Advice.                       
OL,18,FIncreasing numbers of people are being 
OL,19,Fleft without heat or light when they   
OL,20,Fare unable to afford meter top-ups.    
